replies.body:
Irregular latency (ping) is often the result of routing issues to a specific server. This would be why you could have a good connection to some servers or games but not another. Before we take a look at your route, I'd like you to ensure your local network settings are aligned with our [connection guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if those steps caused any change in your latency.
